  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvN2U0NGRjODIwZTVlMDk4YWNhNzljLmpwZz93aWR0aD01MDAmaGVpZ2h0PTM2NA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7e44dc820e5e098aca79c.jpg?width=500&amp;height=364\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7e44dc820e5e098aca79c.jpg?width=500&amp;height=364\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7e44dc820e5e098aca79c.jpg?width=500&amp;height=364\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93b3JkcHJlc3MuY29tL3Bvc3RzL2xhdGV3cml0ZS53b3JkcHJlc3MuY29t\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://wordpress.com/posts/latewrite.wordpress.com\">我本是賭檔里懶散滴人</a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n因近日仇美反日情緒高漲，日本人反了，大年三十竟唱起了「楊白勞：我本是賭檔里懶散滴人」。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n（開篇還是大雪）<br/>\r\n喜兒：<br/>\r\n北風那個吹<br/>\r\n雪花那個飄<br/>\r\n雪花那個飄飄<br/>\r\n年來到<br/>\r\n…<br/>\r\n（開始走味）<br/>\r\n爹爹好賭骰子台<br/>\r\n整七那個天<br/>\r\n三十那個晚上<br/>\r\n也不回還<br/>\n<br/>\r\n我念老天別太成全<br/>\r\n想愛賭滴爹爹我心慌亂<br/>\r\n我怕那賭鬼回家轉<br/>\r\n愁眉苦臉過啥子年<br/>\r\n愁眉苦臉過啥子年<br/>\n<br/>\r\n楊白勞：<br/>\r\n人家閨女有花戴<br/>\r\n你爹我輸得剩麻袋<br/>\r\n扯來了二尺紅頭繩<br/>\r\n回得家來把喜兒騙<br/>\r\n哎，來把我滴喜兒騙<br/>\n<br/>\r\n喜兒：<br/>\r\n賣豆腐賺那幾個錢<br/>\r\n本想稱它回二斤面<br/>\r\n賭鬼滴爹爹不顧家<br/>\r\n在外頭狂賭好幾天<br/>\n<br/>\r\n人家閨女有花戴<br/>\r\n俺家滴家底全挨上<br/>\r\n爹爹他光腚把家轉<br/>\r\n紅頭繩呀他拿我騙<br/>\r\n哎，該死滴爹爹他把我騙<br/>\n<br/>\r\n黨聽不下去啦，唱：<br/>\r\n家家滴閨女要花戴<br/>\r\n家家滴水缸要鍋蓋<br/>\r\n戴花架不住死耍賴<br/>\r\n欠債扯蛋給誰看<br/>\r\n階級成分該怎麼改<br/>\r\n嗯，賭徒服管<br/>\r\n就算他個貧下中乞丐<br/>\n<br/>\r\n美帝國主義也蠢蠢欲動，唱：<br/>\r\n門神門神騎著馬<br/>\r\n豆腐大刀一塊耍<br/>\r\n…<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93b3JkcHJlc3MuY29tL3Bvc3RzL2xhdGV3cml0ZS53b3JkcHJlc3MuY29t\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://wordpress.com/posts/latewrite.wordpress.com\">我本是賭檔里懶散滴人</a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n© All rights reserved by latewrite.\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
